cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.IR 

This paper involves the use of machine learning models for regression prediction and analysis on high dimensional data, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the focus on employee theft and dishonesty suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of feature selection techniques and data embedding techniques suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the focus on identifying and managing risky employees suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
